304
00:19:14,510 --> 00:19:15,510
Kalian semua pergilah.

305
00:19:16,190 --> 00:19:17,190
Dewa Agung, Anda…

306
00:19:17,190 --> 00:19:17,910
Pergi!

307
00:19:20,800 --> 00:19:25,000
♪Pada akhirnya akan mengaku padamu♪

308
00:19:25,670 --> 00:19:26,390
Sepuluh ribu tahun lalu,

309
00:19:26,670 --> 00:19:27,840
